          },
          "reviewBody": "Francis was good 5 years ago but now their teachers are below average specially after class2. No parent says thy are happy. They give too.many leaves and extend exams unnecessarily. Their teachers make kids watch movie in class so that silence is maintained. So many students changed school in 2025 and 2026 because they couldn't recruit teachers. Kids are sitting in class watching walls.its worse than govt skool.now.",
          "publisher": {
