          "datePublished": "2023-08-25",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Nice school. There is bond created here with teachers and students. Various competitions are held for skill development. Teachers are much friendly here. Junior grades are also provided with smart classes. Discipline and behaviour is must. They try to solve the issues of child in every single point. Staff is cooperative and all content for easy access is provided on app. Thanks",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "St Francis School - Abhay Khand,Indirapuram"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "amit Chawla"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-08-09",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I got my daughter (8yrs) admitted to swimming summer camp in may 2023. The 6 weeks time spent have been very amazing. The quality of pool, Maintenace, discipline and above all the coaches has been much more than a satisfying. Being the first time in this sport, my daughter won bronze medal at the end of summer camp. It has been all out of the focus, dedication, expertise and teaching technique of the coaches that has made my daughter a good swimmer. Looking at the performance and satisfaction my daughter has extended the tenure for further 3 months. Moreover, myself have also been motivated and have joined the academy. Now with one month or so, I am also enjoying the sport and seems like I have been swimming for years now. This personal attention by the coaches (all of them) have been the sole reason for my and my daughter success and happiness. Many thank you SFS coaches for this kind of guidance and support. I encourage ppl to join and specially the beginners.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "St Francis School - Abhay Khand,Indirapuram"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Anureet Bamrah"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-03-05",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi all , my both kids have been studying in this school from last many years  and I must say that its the best school in Indirapuram.  The teachers and other staff is very cooperative .  They always try to enhance the kids for their overall development.  School has seven Matras  and recalling it every morning is the best which I think it is the most appropriate way to teach kids to be a better human. Even their annual function themes are also  very appreciable and informative.. last year it was about unity in diversity.. and this year its our mother earth . The teachers always try to give their best in kid's learning  . Worth and best decision we took for our kids to make them study here . Thanks.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
