          "reviewBody": "My daughter has studied in SFS indirapuram. She absolutely loves the school and the staff. Her teachers are a great encouragement and and the academic program is great.\nI really want to appreciate all the Teachers / staff of the St. Francis School for bringing out the best of our kids during the Annual day celebration held on 28th Feb 2023.",
          "publisher": {
